==Books==
Esumi has released two artistic nude photo books: &quot;Esumi&quot; in October 1996 (, Little More); and &quot;E-Mode&quot; in November 1999 (, Little More). She has also published two works of literature: an autobiography titled , published in December 1997 (, Kadokawa Shoten) and reprinted in July 1999 (, Kadokawa Shoten); and an essay titled , published in March 2006 (, Shueisha).

