=== IKARUS low level console ===
Press at a serial console (115200 baud) while booting.
* a &lt;addr&gt; address
* b
* c CPU PVR value
* g &lt;&gt; go
* i &lt;&gt; in
* l
* m memory size?
* o &lt;&gt; out
* q shutdown
* r read
* s
* v
* w &lt;32 bit value&gt; write
* x exit
* z
* inc address
* dec address
 =B00000000,I00,O00;

